<HEADLINE> Lesotho's Election Date Postponed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, June 9 (Xinhua) -- Lesotho's Deputy Prime
Minister Kelebone Maope announced in the capital of Maseru on
Friday that Elections scheduled to take place in the country next
March will be delayed.
</P>
