<HEADLINE> Giraffe Sets Record in Giving Birth </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Andan, the mother, became the first giraffe artificially bred
by a Chinese zoo in 1978. She was born in the Beijing Zoo and
moved to the Taiyuan Zoo in 1981.
</P>
<P>
Since 1983, Andan has given births to two male and five female
cubs. The newly-born cub, not the result of artificial breeding,
was a girl.
</P>
