<HEADLINE> International Neck Tumor Conference Opens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 9 (Xinhua) -- The Year 2000 International
Conference on Head and Neck Tumors opened in Shanghai today.
</P>
<P>
More than 300 medical experts from 22 countries and regions are
participating in the four-day conference, and will deliver over
300 papers.
</P>
<P>
