<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, June 9 (Xinhua) -- The Sensitive Index (Sensex) rose
slightly on the Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE) Friday following fresh
buying support from speculators as well as Financial Institutions.
</P>
