<P>
The exams aim to build a more highly-trained team of
prosecutors, SPP officials said. There are about 7,200 procurator
vacancies across the country, which will be filled with those who
pass the national exams.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, procuratorates at all levels will be streamlined,
and unqualified employees will lose their jobs, the official said.
</P>
<P>
Qiu Xueqiang, head of the Political Department of the SPP said
that at least three chief procurators under 45 will be employed in
every procuratorate in the country. Chief procuratorates will
serve a limited period before being moved to another post. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
