international dignitaries at previous events will be deployed at
the venue of the meetings, which will also be their residence
during the nine-day forums," Savek said.
</P>
<P>
He believed that the upcoming meeting and related forums would
pass smoothly and successfully as other previous international
conferences held here, paving the way for Thailand to be selected
as the host of world forums in the future.
</P>
<P>
Asked if the security officers had been prepared for possible
rallies and movements of interest groups during the period, he
said that preparations had been in place and that he believed
rallies, if any, would be within the framework of law and order.
</P>
