Monday and Tuesday, and came to Cairo on Wednesday. The
Palestinians and Israel have agreed to resume their final-status
negotiations near Washington next week for a final peace agreement
planned for September 13.
</P>
<P>
Arafat will listen to Mubarak's views on the latest developments
and seek means of pushing forward the peace process which is
faltering because of Israeli evasive tactics, al-Qedra was quoted
as saying by Egypt's Middle East News Agency.
</P>
