", said China's urbanization level increased to 30.9 percent in
1999, up one percentage point over 1998.
</P>
<P>
-- Doctors at a hospital in Susong County of east China's Anhui
Province successfully separated a 49-day-old siamese twin, who
were connected at the buttocks, sacroiliac, and rectum.
