<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary at 0010 GMT, June 9 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM -- The Israeli and Palestinian negotiation teams for
the so-called back-channel talks had been holding "private
conversations" in the past few days on the status of Jerusalem,
Israel's Army Radio reported.
</P>
<P>
