in order to improve the investment climate in the country,"
Kasyanov said.
</P>
<P>
He is convinced that a government economic program with "the
important ideas" of the Center for Strategic Development taken
into account will be adopted by the end of June. But the cabinet
should take some necessary measures to accelerate the economic
improvement before this document comes into effect, Kasyanov said.
</P>
<P>
The premier is very much encouraged by the State Duma's (the
lower house of the parliament) support for the government's
initiative to introduce a single income tax scale.
</P>
<P>
He expressed hope that the lawmakers will endorse a single
social tax bill formulated by the cabinet as a measure to keep the
budget revenues' stable growth.
</P>
<P>
The Prime Minister also promised to make efforts to ease the
tax burden of the population. 
