<HEADLINE> Virgin Atlantic To Screen Games Onboard </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, June 9 (Xinhua) -- Virgin Atlantic Airways Friday
announced that it will be the first and only airline screening all
of the England football team's Euro 2000 matches onboard.
</P>
<P>
The company said it will be broadcasting the matches in
association with sportal.co.uk. and Orange over its inflight
entertainment system the day after the match has been played on
all longhaul routes.
</P>
