those matches will also be screened. Regardless of whether England
makes it to the final, the match will be screened onboard on July
3, according to the announcement.
</P>
<P>
Each Virgin Atlantic passenger has their own seat-back
television screen which means that those who are not football
crazy can watch up to twenty alternative channels. 
